[RELEASE] Set up local development environment with PCF Dev
---
install virtualBox
#### What?

VirtualBox is a tool used by vagrant & PCF Dev to create and manage virtual machines on your development environment.

#### How?
Install the VirtualBox from https://www.virtualbox.org/


#### Expected Result
```
$ VBoxManage --version
5.1.2r108956
```
L: core tools
